FBIS3-31723 "dreeu036_y_94003" FBIS-EEU-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Feb 1994 YUGOSLAVIA Federal Nikola Sainovic Appointed Vice President LD2202154894 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in Serbo-Croatian 1426 GMT 22 Feb 94 LD2202154894 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service Language: Serbo-Croatian Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Belgrade, 22 Feb (TANJUG) -- Federal Assembly President Radoje Kontic has decided to appoint Nikola Sainovic, the hitherto president of the Government of Serbia, vice president of the federal government, the Federal Information Ministry reported today. Sainovic will, in his capacity as vice president of the federal government, coordinate work on the implementation of a program for the reconstruction of the monetary system and the economic recovery of the Federal Republic of Yugoslavia. [passage omitted]
